\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {4}{\ignorespaces Rank score $R(S,t)$ under four weight functions after staking stops (dashed vertical). Accumulation rank never decays, allowing old content to permanently dominate the feed. Exponential and power-law decay gracefully derank stale content; the step window hard-resets at boundary $W$.}}{8}{figure.caption.4}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:ranking_decay}{{4}{8}{Rank score $R(S,t)$ under four weight functions after staking stops (dashed vertical). Accumulation rank never decays, allowing old content to permanently dominate the feed. Exponential and power-law decay gracefully derank stale content; the step window hard-resets at boundary $W$}{figure.caption.4}{}}
