\@writefile{lof}{\contentsline {figure}{\numberline {6}{\ignorespaces Smoothed curator ROI as a function of arrival fraction across four values of $\alpha $ (uniform stake distribution, $n=60$). The break-even crossing (ROI = 0) shifts leftward as $\alpha $ decreases, shrinking the profitable participation window. Higher $\alpha $ is necessary but not sufficient for broad curator participation.}}{11}{figure.caption.6}\protected@file@percent }
\newlabel{fig:roi_phase}{{6}{11}{Smoothed curator ROI as a function of arrival fraction across four values of $\alpha $ (uniform stake distribution, $n=60$). The break-even crossing (ROI = 0) shifts leftward as $\alpha $ decreases, shrinking the profitable participation window. Higher $\alpha $ is necessary but not sufficient for broad curator participation}{figure.caption.6}{}}
